o uniquely infer the spectrum of the\nspin-wave in the domain-wall nanochannel once we know both the injection and\nthe transmitted waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Nov 2017 03:16:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Mar 2018 01:35:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-21"}
